OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry through much of the day
OL,6,Fwith some bright spells possible in
OL,7,Fthe east in the morning. Otherwise
OL,8,Flargely cloudy with a few spots of
OL,9,Frain in the west in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be cloudy in the
OL,12,Fevening with some patchy light rain,
OL,13,Fmainly in the west. Staying mostly
OL,14,Fcloudy overnight with further spots of
OL,15,Flight rain at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FCloudy through the day,
OL,18,Fwarmer with the best chance of bright
OL,19,For sunny spells in the east. Further
OL,20,Fpatchy light rain in the west, mainly
OL,21,Fdry in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
